      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical opportunity for a value-minded buyer who wants dependable basic transportation at an accessible price. It shows wear consistent with age and use, but it still offers solid potential as a budget commuter, backup vehicle, or starter project. If you\u2019re looking for low-cost entry into ownership without unnecessary hype, this is a sensible choice with real value.",
