    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a project, or a handy spare vehicle. It\u2019s priced to sell and could be a great fit for a buyer who doesn\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC. If you want something cheap, straightforward, and full of possibility, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 4800.0,
