      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough-running used car with a solid drivetrain foundation and plenty of life left for the right buyer. Starts, moves, and has the kind of honest mechanical character that makes it a great budget commuter, shop spare, or weekend fixer. Not cosmetically perfect and shows its age, but it\u2019s been kept serviceable and offers a strong value for someone who wants dependable basic transportation without spending big. Priced to sell and worth a look if you appreciate a vehicle with usable bones and straightforward mechanicals.",
      "price": 5950.0,
